{
  "stem": "1581.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, he had connections in his profession.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he was able, through his connections, to get visa in very strange countries, whether it was Bulgaria or Ecuador or Peru or Cuba.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he got quite a bit of people out.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He himself had two visas in his pocket and was ready to leave.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But he was held back.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because he had wanted to help our mother to get out first.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we-- I-- there were three places, which were more or less accessible for Jews at that time.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In the whole wild-- wide world, there were three places.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "One was Shanghai, which-- where the Chinese established a kind of a Jewish settlement.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And if you could get there, which of course was no easy task, you could stay there.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Lots of my friends stayed in and survived in Shanghai.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The second place was Santo Domingo, who-- there was a little town called Sosua.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And a few hundred Jews managed to get to Sosua.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And Trujillo, at that time, the guy in charge in Santo Domingo--",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Was looking for a middle class.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--Wanted to get the Jews in, because they were good citizens.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the third one was to go illegally to Palestine.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That means to have a knapsack over your shoulder and walk through Slovakia and through Romania and through Turkey--",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was not a Zionist.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I was willing to go to Palestine.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I was held back by my mother, because she was in no condition-- she was an elderly lady-- to go through all this.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My wife and I, we would have been willing to go.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I was in Brno.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
